race.description: Book Corporate Xmas Party Trackside 21 Dec Plate
race.comment: The well-related REGGIE'S FOLLY (3) (half to G1 winner Heavens Above) was a narrow winner two back at this track then out of the money last time when fourth here. Drops a little in the weights and can return to winning form. FRIEND IN NEED (9) has been in the placings at her last two, most recently when third over 1550m at Murwillumbah at her third run back from a break. The winkers have been removed for this and expected to be in the finish. DENETTA (5) missed the placings two runs back then did well last start but found one better over 1666m at Ipswich, beaten only 0.7 lengths. Perfectly placed and is sure to prove tough to beat. FOUR ACE (2) has been safely held at his last couple of runs, the latest when he was always well back and never really threatened, finishing tenth over 1300m at Toowoomba. Better than the last couple of runs suggest. Can feature.
